Troubleshooting Tips
Import errors: Ensure you're running tests from the project root directory and virtual environment is activated

Decimal precision issues: Always use Decimal for monetary calculations, not float

Fixture not found: Check that fixtures are defined in the same test class or in conftest.py

Coverage not showing: Verify the --cov path matches your source directory structure

Tests passing but coverage low: Check for untested edge cases and error conditions

